  "notes": "Public TUM-VI sanity lane for the upstream monocular fisheye path using the official EuRoC export of room1 at 512x512/16-bit. room1 was chosen because the room sequences publish full motion-capture ground truth for the entire trajectory, the 512_16 export is smaller than the 1024_16 variant for a practical clean-room rerun, and cam0 matches the single-camera upstream mono_tum_vi contract."
